    <h2>Vision Statement</h2>
    <p>The vision of Abundant Faith Fellowship Church is to build a community of individuals who desire to experience God’s abundance in every area of their lives (spirit, soul, mind, and body).
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-6">
    <h2>Mission Statement</h2>
    <p>The mission of Abundant Faith Fellowship Church is to spread the Gospel of Christ to the unsaved, maintain the worship of God, and inspire in all persons a love for Christ, a passion for righteousness, and a consciousness of their duties to God and their fellow man. We pledge our lives to Christ and covenant with each other to demonstrate His Spirit through worship, witnessing, and ministering to the needs of the people of this church and the community.</p>
  </div>
